    CLR.L   D2                          CLEAR D1
    MOVE.L  #$001B8FDD,D1               store the hex for the colour WHITE in d1
    MOVE.B  #21,D0                      Load 4 into D0
    TRAP    #15                         Runs Trap 21 which changes the colour of the text to the colour stored in D1
